                     <interp inst="t18260406-160-off854" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18260406-160-cd855" type="crimeDate">3d of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-160-off854 t18260406-160-cd855"></join>, 3 frocks, value 10s.; 4 aprons, value 2s.; 2 pinafores, value 1s.; 1 petticoat, value 1s., and 1 frill, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18260406-160-victim896" type="victimName">
                  Jane 
                  Riley
               <interp inst="t18260406-160-victim896" type="surname" value="Riley"></interp>
